00:00:41.660 --> 00:00:43.660
What's the difference and use between

00:00:43.660 --> 00:00:45.500
Baking soda and baking powder?

00:00:46.114 --> 00:00:48.114
So the difference is

00:00:50.460 --> 00:00:52.460
baking power is like yeast, it will help your dough rise

00:00:53.075 --> 00:00:55.075
baking soda helps keep your bakes moist

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:02.880
you can also use it to clean you house :) your fridge and so on

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:09.880
I personally add like a tsp in my cakes 

00:01:11.420 --> 00:01:13.420
